3.5	ROOT	S . # More sentences should be declarative sentences.
1	ROOT	S !
0.5	ROOT	is it true that S ? # Less sentence have this structure.

1	S	NP VP
1	VP	Verb NP
1	NP	Det Noun
0.2	NP	NP PP # As shown in 2d, 0.5 makes sentences shorter, yet it leads to
# too many Prep in the sentence. A smaller number like 0.2 makes the sentence
# more natural.
1	PP	Prep NP
3	Noun	Adj Noun # As shown in 2d, 6 allows multiple Adjs come before a
# Noun. However, because the size of Adj vocabulary is small, it is highly
# likely that a Noun has a Adj coming before it more than once. So a small 
# number like 3 makes the sentence more natural.

